Make Count be 1
Change Count to Count plus 1
Expect Count is 2

Make Maybe Name be nothing as Maybe String
Change Maybe Name to "Ada"
Match Maybe Name
  When Some Name
    Expect Name is "Ada"
  When nothing
    Expect false is true

Record Profile
  Has Name as String
  Has Age as Int

Make Ada be New Profile with Name be "Ada" and Age be 36
Change Name of Ada to "Ada Lovelace"
Change Age of Ada to Age of Ada plus 1
Expect Name of Ada is "Ada Lovelace"
Expect Age of Ada is 37
